<p><a name="Footnotes_and_references" id="Footnotes_and_references"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Augusto_Pinochet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Footnotes and references">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Footnotes and references</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-Name-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Name_0-0" title="">^</a></b> Pinochet pronounced his name with a silent t (although it is not uncommon for the t to be pronounced by local Spanish speakers).</li>
